# 預設:自動正規化文字檔,倉庫內統一存 LF(消除跨機 CRLF/LF 警告與 diff 噪音)
* text=auto

# 依平台慣例固定行尾
*.sh   text eol=lf
*.mjs  text eol=lf
*.cmd  text eol=crlf
*.bat  text eol=crlf
*.ps1  text eol=crlf

# 明確二進位(不做行尾/diff 處理)
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.webp  binary
*.avif  binary
*.onnx  binary
*.sqlite binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf   binary

# GitHub linguist:設計文件 / mockup 不計入語言統計,讓語言比例反映 C#/TypeScript
docs/**            linguist-documentation
docs/mockups/*.html linguist-documentation
